flowchart TD
  Start([Enter Maventor]) --> Landing[Open Mentee Dashboard]
  Landing --> HasProfile{Profile complete?}
  HasProfile -- No --> Profile[Complete Mentee Profile]
  Profile --> SaveProfile[Save Skills and Goals]
  SaveProfile --> WaitPairing[Wait for Officer Pairing]
  HasProfile -- Yes --> PairCheck{Pairing assigned?}
  WaitPairing --> PairCheck

  PairCheck -- No --> PairingPending[View Pending Status]
  PairingPending --> RefreshStatus[Refresh or return later]
  RefreshStatus --> PairCheck

  PairCheck -- Yes --> ActivePair[Open Active Pairing]
  ActivePair --> Chat[Send and Read Messages]
  ActivePair --> Goals[Create or Update Milestones]
  ActivePair --> CheckIn[Submit Reflection Check-In]
  CheckIn --> Survey[Complete Pulse Survey]
  Survey --> Progress[View Progress and Compatibility Trend]
  Goals --> Progress
  Chat --> Progress
  Progress --> End([Continue Mentorship Cycle])
